### 前后端联调测试（第23次课）
### 此文件通过 Vite 代理访问前端 API，路径带 /api/ 前缀
### Vite 代理会自动 rewrite：/api/xxx → /xxx（后端实际路径）

### ========== 环境变量 ==========
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ========== 1. 商品相关接口（公开，无需Token）==========

### 获取所有商品
GET http://localhost:5173/api/products
Accept: application/json

### 获取分类列表
GET http://localhost:5173/api/categories
Accept: application/json

### 分页查询商品
GET http://localhost:5173/api/products/page?page=1&pageSize=4
Accept: application/json

### 根据ID获取商品
GET http://localhost:5173/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

### 搜索商品
GET http://localhost:5173/api/products/search?keyword=手机
Accept: application/json

### ========== 2. 用户相关接口 ==========

### 用户注册
POST http://localhost:5173/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser2",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "13900139000",
  "email": "test2@example.com",
  "address": "上海市浦东新区"
}

### 用户登录
POST http://localhost:5173/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser2",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ========== 3. 购物车相关接口（需要Token）==========

### 添加商品1到购物车
POST http://localhost:5173/api/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### 添加商品2到购物车
POST http://localhost:5173/api/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": 2,
  "quantity": 1
}

### 获取购物车列表
GET http://localhost:5173/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 更新购物车数量（cart_id=1改为3件）
PUT http://localhost:5173/api/cart/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "newQuantity": 3
}

### 更新勾选状态（选中）
PUT http://localhost:5173/api/cart/1/selected
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "selected": 1
}

### 全选
PUT http://localhost:5173/api/cart/selected/batch
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "selected": 1
}

### 获取购物车数量
GET http://localhost:5173/api/cart/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取已勾选商品数
GET http://localhost:5173/api/cart/selected/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========== 4. 订单相关接口（需要Token）==========

### 创建订单
POST http://localhost:5173/api/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "张三",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳区建国路100号"
}

### 获取订单详情（orderId=1）
GET http://localhost:5173/api/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 下载订单发票（orderId=1）
GET http://localhost:5173/api/invoice/download/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
